Ingredient: mozzarella sticks, each cut into 6 pieces
glutinous sweet rice flour (such as Mochiko)
ground cinnamon, or more to taste
bananas (ripe or very ripe work best)
fresh blueberries - rinsed, drained and patted dry
fresh pitted and quartered sweet cherries
frozen chopped spinach - thawed, drained, and squeezed dry
white sugar, or more to taste
